{"tid":185309,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【#Your】醜女做甚麼都是錯","createTime":"2017-04-03T11:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T11:38:34.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"776d24ae7e6e1f9a38e8cf4e52ced94ebe784aa8","tid":185309,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"「女人生得醜唔一定係輸家」<br />\n咁你都信？？？<br />\n<br />\n逢週一播放的網台AbemaTV節目「Busu Television」，<br />\n就告訴大家一個殘酷的事實－醜女無論做甚麼，在得不到旁人歡心。<br />\n<br />\n這次做的街訪環節，<br />\n找來日本街頭的路人訪問他們在聯誼酒會上實際遇過的「ブス（Busu）」（醜女，不論是外表或性格上）。<br />\n<br />\n在日本人眼中，到底有哪種女生會被判為「ブス」？<br />\n<br />\n奧斯卡最佳女主角型：<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201704/Wrir8J2J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201704%2FWrir8J2J.jpg&h=2bee8048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲平常絕對不會幫大家分餸菜（e.g.沙律），在聯誼酒會卻拼了老命在分沙律賣弄「女子力」的女生。<br />\n<br />\n牡丹雖好還需綠葉扶持型：<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201704/jWIg0xzF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201704%2FjWIg0xzF.jpg&h=91659329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲特地將長得醜的都叫來，（以比較法突顯自己美貌的）才是（心靈）最醜陋的。<br />\n<br />\n上面兩種還算內涵醜陋的類型，<br />\n那麼如果被歸納為外表醜陋的女生，心裡OS又會有如何分別呢？<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201704/HhUKu2ST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201704%2FHhUKu2ST.jpg&h=41a94556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲明明長得醜，卻又不主動為大家分沙津。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201704/jq8YChbK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201704%2Fjq8YChbK.jpg&h=f2caa0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「在男女聯誼活動上，可愛女生就是擔當與男性談天說地的角色。」<br />\n　「而醜女，只需在暗角幫大家分食物就對了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201704/hcDW5TLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201704%2FhcDW5TLU.jpg&h=53b57fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「明明是醜女，埋單時候卻不乖乖拿出銀包。」<br />\n　「長得醜的話，好歹也應該付一點錢吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201704/m35UFsXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201704%2Fm35UFsXA.jpg&h=0ffc319e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲還記得炸雞應否淋檸檬汁的爭拗嗎？<br />\n　的確有些人是不愛擠檸檬的，不過還得看為你服務是誰人。<br />\n　「雖然可愛女生與醜女同時在場，想不到竟然是醜的那個來幫我擠檸檬汁。『為何要用你的手弄髒我準備放入口的食物？？？』」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201704/6fGh0J1l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201704%2F6fGh0J1l.jpg&h=bcd559bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲最極端的，連「自身存在」都是個問題。<br />\n　「有醜女在場的話，美酒味道也會立即降至一半以下。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=4963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D4963&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik6S6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=ec90642a\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=4963</a>"},{"pid":"8f421eab595c0c45e0e580c743e9231fc7e9c438","tid":185309,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:38:34.000Z","msg":"而家咩年代<br />\n<br />\n飛一次韓國解決到所有問題啦"}]}